    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>本来打算用手机显示从麦克风输入的电压波形，之后秉着先实现基本功能的原则，所以没做产生信号那一部分，仅仅是将波形画了出来。</p></blockquote><h2 id="功能描述：页面上有一块网格区域和三个按钮，网格区域代表示波器图形显示界面，通过按下不同按钮选择显示正弦波，方波和三角波。"><a href="#功能描述：页面上有一块网格区域和三个按钮，网格区域代表示波器图形显示界面，通过按下不同按钮选择显示正弦波，方波和三角波。" class="headerlink" title="功能描述：页面上有一块网格区域和三个按钮，网格区域代表示波器图形显示界面，通过按下不同按钮选择显示正弦波，方波和三角波。"></a>功能描述：页面上有一块网格区域和三个按钮，网格区域代表示波器图形显示界面，通过按下不同按钮选择显示正弦波，方波和三角波。</h2><p>这里值得一提的是示波器的图形显示界面，我们采用SurfaceView来实现它。</p><h2 id="SurfaceView是什么？"><a href="#SurfaceView是什么？" class="headerlink" title="SurfaceView是什么？"></a>SurfaceView是什么？</h2><p>SurfaceView 提供了专用于绘制的Surface，你可以控制此Surface的大小和尺寸; SurfaceView负责将Surface放置在屏幕上的正确位置。Surface 是纵深排序的(Z-Ordered),且总是位于当前窗口的后面，SurfaceView提供一个区域，确保Surface能在且只能在这一区域可见。当其他控件堆叠显示于Surface上时，控件将遮盖相关区域；如果控件透明时，每次更新Surface都要对遮盖的区域进行透明效果计算，但请注意，它会对性能产生影响。<br>简单来讲，SurfaceView提供了画布(Surface)，我们只需要在画布上绘制内容。</p><h2 id="使用SurfaceView的步骤"><a href="#使用SurfaceView的步骤" class="headerlink" title="使用SurfaceView的步骤"></a>使用SurfaceView的步骤</h2><ul><li>获取SurfaceHolder对象，用他来访问和控制SurfaceView底层的Surface。</li></ul><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mSurfaceHolder = getHolder();</span><br><span class="line">mSurfaceHolder.addCallback(<span class="keyword">this</span>);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><p>新建一个线程并重写run函数用来绘图</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mThread = <span class="keyword">new</span> Thread(<span class="keyword">new</span> Runnable() &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="meta">@Override</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">run</span><span class="params">()</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">//绘图代码 </span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>绘图代码，用lockCanvas获取当前界面的内容，并返回一个Canvas对象，得到绘图的画布，最后通过unlockCanvasAndPost方法更新到当前界面。</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Canvas canvas = mSurfaceHolder.lockCanvas();</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 使用canvas绘制内容 </span></span><br><span class="line">mSurfaceHolder.unlockCanvasAndPost(canvas);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>在surfaceCreated函数中启动线程</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Override</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">surfaceCreated</span><span class="params">(SurfaceHolder holder)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    mThread.start();      </span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h2 id="虚拟示波器"><a href="#虚拟示波器" class="headerlink" title="虚拟示波器"></a>虚拟示波器</h2><ul><li><p>在xml中摆放RadioButton和SurfaceView控件</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">SurfaceView</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">    <span class="attr">android:id</span>=<span class="string">"@+id/sfv"</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">    <span class="attr">android:layout_width</span>=<span class="string">"match_parent"</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">    <span class="attr">android:layout_height</span>=<span class="string">"593dp"</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">RadioGroup</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">    <span class="attr">android:id</span>=<span class="string">"@+id/rg"</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">    <span class="attr">android:layout_width</span>=<span class="string">"match_parent"</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">    <span class="attr">android:layout_hei